  </head>
  <body>
    <p style="font-weight: normal">
      <font face="Courier New, monospace">Hello &lt;managers name&gt;, </font>
    </p>
    <p style="font-weight: normal"><font face="Courier New, monospace">On
        <b>&lt;date&gt;</b> it was discovered there is a potential
        shadow I.T. asset within ticket:
        <b>&lt;ticket number&gt;.</b> </font>
    </p>
    <p><font face="Courier New, monospace"><span
          style="font-weight: normal">The initial investigation has been
          completed. At this time, no confirmed business owner or
          accountable unit has been identified as the owner of the asset</span></font></p>
    <p><font face="Courier New, monospace"><span
          style="font-weight: normal">To ensure proper governance and
          risk management, we are requesting business escalation to
          determine one or more of the following:</span></font></p>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <p style="font-weight: normal"><font
            face="Courier New, monospace">Potential owner of the asset.</font></p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p style="font-weight: normal"><font
            face="Courier New, monospace">Potentially have security
            controls installed on the device / asset.</font></p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p style="font-weight: normal"><font
            face="Courier New, monospace">Assign potential risk to the
            owning party, shareholder, stakeholder or business unit.</font></p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p style="font-weight: normal"><font
            face="Courier New, monospace">Have the device disconnected
            from the network within the allowable 30 day window. </font>
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p style="font-weight: normal"><font
            face="Courier New, monospace">Remove the device after the
            window has been exceeded. </font> </p>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <p style="font-weight: normal"><font face="Courier New, monospace">Please
        advise on the next steps or provide direction on how you would
        like
        for the SOC to proceed.</font></p>
    <p style="font-weight: normal"><br>
      <br>
    </p>
    <p style="font-weight: normal"><font face="Courier New, monospace">Thank
        you, </font>
    </p>
    <p style="font-weight: normal"><font face="Courier New, monospace">SOC
        Team.</font></p>
